About Algodon Wines & Luxury Development Group
Diversified Collection of Luxury Assets Anchored by Non-Leveraged Argentina Real Estate Holdings.Algodon Wines & Luxury Development Group, Inc. (Algodon Group) is a U.S. based public company that owns and develops luxury real estate assets in Argentina.  We are among the first real estate developers in Argentina to report on a U.S. stock market (OTCQB: VINO), and our non-leveraged assets provide one of the few public vehicles to participate in the anticipated growth in value of Argentina real estate. Algodon Group is the only publicly traded luxury development brand with unleveraged real estate, premium wines, and luxury lifestyle assets currently focused on Argentina.Algodon seeks to become the LVMH of South America with our initial collection of assets beginning in Argentina, due to its value proposition and current opportunities.  Algodon is an emerging luxury brand, currently consisting of a collection of offerings that includes Algodon Fine Wines, Algodon Wine Estates, Algodon Wine & Wellness Resort, Algodon Mansion, and Algodon Extra Virgin Olive Oil.  Our mission is to utilize the value inherent in our non-leveraged luxury assets and real estate as a base to roll up and acquire additional assets directly related to the future growth of our brand. Algodon's winemakers work diligently towards the goal of our brand becoming synonymous with the best Malbec and Malbec blends in the world, which we believe may significantly advance the value of the Algodon luxury brand; one of quality, elegance and attention to detail.  With our fines wines as our ambassador, we identify and develop unique lifestyle properties, vineyard operations and other real estate assets, as well as luxury brands in Argentina, and may potentially expand in the future to other vital areas of South America and around the globe. We are opportunistic investors with an entrepreneurial spirit and a contrarian investment philosophy.Our current luxury portfolio includes the vineyards and winery of Algodon Wine Estates in San Rafael, Mendoza, which has received international accolades for Algodon Fine Wines, and which includes 325 acres (131 hectares) of vines dating back to 1946, as well as a 2,050 acre (830 hectare) luxury real estate development with over 400 estate lots (ranging from .5 to 7 acres), and Algodon Wines & Wellness Resort, a developing premier wine, wellness, culinary, and sport resort that includes golf and tennis facilities, an all-suite boutique hotel in Buenos Aires, called Algodon Mansion, located in the heart of the city’s luxury residential and embassy district, and Algodon Olive Oil, the estate grown and award-winning extra virgin olive oil that has been expertly blended to complement our wines.Investing in Argentina before the crowd since 2007, Algodon Wines & Luxury Development Group, Inc. is headquartered in New York City, with offices in Buenos Aires and Mendoza.Why Invest in Argentina?

