			Company Description 
		


                Algodon Wines & Luxury Development Group, Inc. engages in the real estate business. Its portfolio includes resorts, hotels, restaurants, golf and tennis clubs, and winemaking investments. The company was founded by Scott L. Mathis on April 5, 1999 and is headquartered in New York, NY.
            




